      "paragraphs": [
        "Construction options for Loader.",
        "`basePath` is prepended to relative asset paths at fetch time. `cache` accepts one or more CacheStore instances. `cacheStrategy` picks the policy used to consult them — defaults to CacheFirstStrategy (check stores → network → write back). `concurrency` caps the number of simultaneous background-queue fetches (default `6`)."
